title: OEMTOOLS 26133 High Flow 7 Piece Coupler and Plug Kit, 1/4" Body, 3/8" NPT, Quick Connect Air Hose Fittings, Air Tool Fittings, High Flow Air Fittings
features: Great Performance: Conventional air couplers and plugs can be limiting; The air hose fitting kit large interior diameter M style quick connect air hose fittings maximize airflow
Air Tool Versatility: Connect our air compressor fittings and watch your pneumatic nail gun, die grinder, and more perform to their full capacity
Easy Operation: Detach plugs and air tools from high flow hose coupler with ease; Push to lock design makes placing plug style air tool fittings into the air couplers easy
Tight Air Flow Tool: Give pneumatic high torque impact wrenches the maximum power; High flow air fittings have a maximum 300 PSI and one hand push to lock design
Generous High Flow Set: Comes with 4 high flow air fitting M style plugs and 3 hose couplers; Standardized 3/8 NPT; Larger interior diameter is fully capable of 300 PSI
description: Operate your air tools with 3/8 air hose fittings at their maximum PSI with OEMTOOLS 26133 High Flow 7 Piece Coupler and Plug Kit, 1/4 inch Body, 3/8 inch NPT. Your standard M-style air hose connectors and air tool connectors won’t let your pneumatic tools work at their highest capacity. This compressor hose connector set comes with male air hose fittings and female fittings. Standard compressor air fittings can leak air, limiting your maximum PSI. But, with this air compressor hose fittings set, your pneumatic cut off tool can work without dips in air flow that occur with standard air hose couplers and plugs. The quick connect coupler has a one hand push-to-lock design that makes changing tools fast and easy. Kit includes: (1) High Flow Plug (1/4 Inch Body, 3/8 Inch FNPT), (1) High Flow Plug (1/4 Inch Body, 3/8 Inch MNPT), (2) High Flow Plugs (1/4 Inch Body, 3/8 Inch FNPT), and (3) High Flow Couplers (1/4 Inch Body, 3/8 Inch MNPT).
